Interface IUser

All Superinterfaces:
Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
CareerStaff, CompanyRep, Student
public interface IUser extends Serializable
Common user interface for entities that have identity and credentials. Implementations represent an application user and must provide accessors for id, name and password, and a mutator for updating the password.
